<h2>The OUPblog</h2>

<p><img class="floatLeft" data-image-id="31c744a5894b66556378" data-image-title="oup-logo-blog.png" data-link-id="a0500b56-fb42-49bd-b732-c6d20439e8a2" data-link-ref="node://10680c37069bed6643a2/982ced22eab1d38d858f/9aa9861ca9bc336adc8b/31c744a5894b66556378" src="https://static.primary.prod.gcms.the-infra.com/static/site/umbrella/image/oup-logo-blog.png?node=31c744a5894b66556378&version=574401:ddd2e3ff040bbd730e04" alt=""  /></p>

<p>The OUPblog offers timely content from our talented authors on nearly every subject, including philosophy, history, science, economics, and more.</p>

